***Twinblade.*** This weapon has a set of blades on either side of its hilt.

**Special.** When you take the Attack action and attack with a twinblade, you can use a bonus action to make another attack with the other end of the weapon, dealing 1d6 slashing damage. You don't add your ability modifier to the damage of the bonus attack, unless that modifier is negative.

